Package com.software.fitness_system.admin_controllers

Class ProgramMonitoringControls

java.lang.Object
com.software.fitness_system.admin_controllers.ProgramMonitoringControls
public class ProgramMonitoringControls extends Object
Provides administrative controls for monitoring fitness program enrollment, generating reports, and tracking the status of programs (Active or Completed). Includes functionalities to display all programs, view enrollment statistics, and generate detailed reports.

This class relies on `ProgramEnrollment` for data representation.

Author: Muath Hassoun
